data.description: Welcome to 2012 Daspit Road - the gem of New Iberia! This gorgeous, 3 bedroom 2 bath, French Style home is situated on a HUGE lot and is conveniently located across from Daspit Elementary. Boasting an open floor plan, a neutral color palate, varied ceiling heights, and wood and tile flooring throughout - this gorgeous home has it all! The beautiful, spacious kitchen is perfect for entertaining and opens to the bright and airy living room and dining room. It also features stainless appliances and an island with a breakfast bar. Moving through the rest of the house, you will notice the master suite and additional bedrooms and bathroom are beautifully kept. The real treat of this property is the sprawling backyard, though! With tons of room for BBQs, birthday parties, a pool, or tons of toys, this impressive backyard is will accommodate! See all this gorgeous home has to offer today! Schedule your showing now! SELLERS ARE WILLIING TO GIVE PAINT ALLOWANCE.
